title: Pixel 5 didn't installs over half of my apps
content: I just upgraded from 4a to 5 via google back (not phone to phone via cable - i may try that next). Everything seemed okay until I scrolled through my home screens and maybe about 30% of the apps I had on my 4a were gone. Does anyone know why this happened?
category: Setting up and Personalizing your Device, Google Pixel 5
